reviewText: Sean Riehl has produced a superior DVD set on Deep Tissue bodywork. He clearly knows his profession and is able to relay it in a clear way that is easy to understand and duplicate.
Great video, very informative and well made.  I would recommend this to massage therapists who are interested to expand their techniques.
I've learned a lot that I've been using in practice from these videos. Narrator is a little monotone though. Good.
